                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The rotting cultist calls out to the Rotting God, offering up their flesh in exchange for power. The rotting cultist is healed @Damage[(4d6+8)[healing]] HP, gains a +1 status bonus on attack rolls for 1 minute, and they reduce any condition (other than slowed) affecting them by 1 (if they have a numerical value; this has no effect on conditions without values). The rotting cultist becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} for 10 minutes as a fungal bloom erupts from their flesh.</p>"
